#Natural Language Processing, Bag of Words
This program uses bag of words algorithm to predict if a customer review is supposed to be positive or negative

Bag of words trains by finding all phrases that tend to appear in relation with a desired value. In this case, the value we are looking for is if the review is positive or negative. All postive reviews create associations with the top most previliant words that are used in postive reviews and the same is done for negative reviews.